41#endif

43# define DUID DBDIR "/duid"
44#endif

47#endif

50#endif

53#endif

56#endif
57#ifndef CONTROLSOCKET
58# define CONTROLSOCKET RUNDIR "/" PACKAGE "%s%s.sock"
59#endif
60#ifndef UNPRIVSOCKET
61# define UNPRIVSOCKET RUNDIR "/" PACKAGE ".unpriv.sock"
62#endif
